  "description": "Product Description:\n\nElevate your elegance with this stunning lab-grown sapphire ring, featuring a timeless halo design and crafted in premium S925 sterling silver. The sterling silver setting is hypoallergenic and resistant to tarnish, offering both beauty and durability for everyday wear.\n\nAt the heart of this ring lies a captivating 9x6.8mm, 2.58-carat oval-cut lab-grown sapphire, radiating a deep blue brilliance that is both alluring and sophisticated. Surrounding the main stone is a double halo of colorless round-cut accent stones, totaling 1.79 carats, which adds a sparkling dimension to this luxurious piece. The ring weighs 4.11 grams and is available in U.S. sizes 5 to 7.5. Please note that lab-grown colored gemstone rings ship within 3-15 days.\n\nKey Features:\n\nLab-Grown Sapphire Center Stone: A 9x6.8mm, 2.58-carat oval-cut gem, showcasing a vivid blue color and remarkable clarity.\n\nHalo Design with Double Row of Accents: Two rows of sparkling, colorless round-cut stones surrounding the sapphire, enhancing its brilliance.\n\nS925 Sterling Silver: Crafted with high-quality, hypoallergenic sterling silver for comfort and durability.\n\nAvailable Sizes: Offered in U.S. ring sizes 5 to 7.5.\n\nShipping: Lab-grown colored gemstone rings are dispatched within 3-15 days.\n\nThis ring embodies timeless beauty and refined elegance, making it a perfect choice for anyone seeking a luxurious statement piece that speaks to modern sophistication.",
